Review Guidelines
To ensure your review is posted on our site, please adhere to the following guidelines:
Star rating, review headline and review text are required fields.
Minimum character limit for review text is five (5) characters.
Maximum character limit for review text is three thousand (3000) characters.
You can upload up to six images (png, gif, jpeg, HEIC or TIFF) with a maximum size of 10MB each.
Focus on the product and your experience with it, both the good and the bad.
Refrain from using inappropriate language.
If you received compensation of any kind in exchange for writing a review, including free or discounted products or services, your review will not be posted to our site.
For issues related to shipping, customer service, availability, pricing, missing items or other concerns, please contact us immediately
here
.
