Terms of Use
as outlined below.
How to Submit a Review
Log in
to your B&H account or
create an account
.
Go to
My Orders
or any product you want to review.
Within the My Orders page, click on See Order Details for the order with the product you want to review. Next to each eligible product there will be a Write a Review button.
On any product page, click the Reviews tab to be taken to the Reviews section. On the right-hand side, there is a Write a Review button.
Click the Write a Review button to begin your review. Select a star rating, enter a review headline, write your review and upload up to six images.
After populating all fields, check to make sure your review is how you want it. Reviews cannot be edited after you click submit.
Click Submit to finish your review.
Your review will be moderated and, if approved, posted to our site within a few days.
